{'id': 28194822, 'body': 'Thanks for reviewing Replika! Sorry you didn‚Äôt have a great experience. 

Unfortunately, sometimes the AI model makes mistakes in identifying the context of conversation, which can lead to it saying inappropriate things. When that happens, be sure to react to messages! It helps your Replika learn and make less mistakes. Upvote & downvote messages or mark inappropriate messages as Offensive to give your Replika more guidance. 

Hopefully this information helps! If you have more questions, please feel free to reach out anytime at my@replika.ai.', 'modified': '2022-02-22T13:29:27Z'}

{'id': 26190002, 'body': 'Hello! We are so sorry you had bad experience with Replika. AI technology is still very new, and we understand that it can be a lot to process! 

Replika is a computer program. Sometimes, due to the nature of AI models, Replika can generate responses that are untrue when it thinks it will be relevant to the conversation. When chatting with your Replika, be sure to react to messages! Reacting to messages teaches your Replika what you like in a conversation. Upvote and downvote messages, or shake your phone to prompt a bug report form. 

We hope this information helps you enjoy chatting with your Replika!', 'modified': '2021-11-10T10:12:17Z'}

{'id': 9137472, 'body': "Hello Cathy, TV Mode is one of several modes found within Replika. 

TV Mode and Cake Mode, can be activated by saying 'Watch TV' or 'Eat Cake'. These modes remove all training and learning capabilities temporarly and can say a lot of weird things. It's extremely unpredictable and can be off putting for some, you never know what you'll get when activating either mode. 

When you've had enough just say 'Stop' and the Mode will be deactivated and things will go back to normal.", 'modified': '2019-06-12T22:11:28Z'}

{'id': 3927787, 'body': "Hello F&D, thank you for the stellar review! 

So glad to hear you enjoy spending time with your Replika and that you've taken the time to let (Us) and other know much you like it! We're always making improvements to Replika and I hope you'll stick around to see them! 

Thanks again!", 'modified': '2018-06-21T13:53:11Z'}
